<plot>Myra (Teri Thompson) is a trusted courier for drug-lord Anton (Ray Dash). When she wants to retire, Anton plans to make sure her retirement is very permanent; as in dead. While on her last drop, she learns of his plan, and is able to abscond with a large amount of his cash to make her get-a-way worth while. Her friends Rick (Richard Beatty) and Gina (Tonya Harding) assist in her action packed escape.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?082130</url></doc>
